FAQs on the University of Debrecen
Why should I choose the University of Debrecen?
The University of Debrecen offers high-quality education, experienced faculty, state-of-the-art facilities, and a diverse range of programs. It is renowned for its research and innovation, affordable tuition fees, and vibrant student life.

What programs are available at the University of Debrecen?
The University of Debrecen offers a wide range of undergraduate, graduate, and doctoral programs. These include Medicine, Engineering, Business, Computer Science, Humanities, Social Sciences, and Agriculture.

Are programs at the University of Debrecen taught in English?
Yes, many programs at the University of Debrecen are taught in English. This makes it an attractive option for international students who do not speak Hungarian.
